Series title in 1971 and '79. In the '79 Series, Stargell hit .400
with three homers and was the Most Valuable Player.
   Sportscaster Lindsey Nelson and sports columnist Jim Murray of
the Los Angeles Times also were honored Sunday during induction
ceremonies at the Hall of Fame.
